1
00:00:11,670 --> 00:00:15,380
[2010]

2
00:00:20,320 --> 00:00:20,870
Zhang.

3
00:00:21,390 --> 00:00:21,990
Good work.

4
00:00:22,070 --> 00:00:23,000
Thank you.

5
00:00:23,640 --> 00:00:24,800
You're calling him Zhang already.

6
00:00:24,800 --> 00:00:25,760
Why act like you've fraternized with him?

7
00:00:25,760 --> 00:00:26,690
Call him Senior.

8
00:00:27,670 --> 00:00:28,760
This girlfriend of yours

9
00:00:28,760 --> 00:00:30,160
is so energetic.

10
00:00:30,440 --> 00:00:31,980
She must've crossed mountains

11
00:00:31,980 --> 00:00:34,520
and ridges to get here
from Jingzhou Police Academy.

12
00:00:34,520 --> 00:00:35,560
What does it mean?

13
00:00:35,790 --> 00:00:37,000
"This girlfriend of yours"?

14
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:38,640
How many girlfriends do you have?

15
00:00:38,640 --> 00:00:40,220
Were you talking about Lili?

16
00:00:40,220 --> 00:00:42,280
Who's Lili? I demand an explanation!

17
00:00:42,280 --> 00:00:44,210
That was just a random expression.

18
00:00:45,880 --> 00:00:46,880
This is for you.

19
00:00:46,900 --> 00:00:48,330
Eat it somewhere.

20
00:00:49,120 --> 00:00:50,150
Do you think I'm a glutton

21
00:00:50,150 --> 00:00:51,000
like you are?

22
00:00:51,880 --> 00:00:53,640
Did you inform your supervisor
of this visit?

23
00:00:53,640 --> 00:00:54,200
All the cadets

24
00:00:54,200 --> 00:00:55,730
are having a free day today.

25
00:00:55,880 --> 00:00:57,000
I was thinking we could...

26
00:00:57,000 --> 00:00:57,670
Don't even.

27
00:00:57,960 --> 00:01:00,110
I have a lot of things to do
at the station later.

28
00:01:00,110 --> 00:01:01,510
I can't keep you company.

29
00:01:03,430 --> 00:01:04,120
Senior.

30
00:01:04,709 --> 00:01:06,840
Is there much work to do at the station?

31
00:01:07,120 --> 00:01:08,640
That's how police stations are.

32
00:01:08,640 --> 00:01:10,140
Try to be more understanding.

33
00:01:10,140 --> 00:01:11,840
You won't see each other often
when you become

34
00:01:11,840 --> 00:01:14,039
a police officer too and raise a family.

35
00:01:14,560 --> 00:01:16,070
Won't see each other often, huh.

36
00:01:16,070 --> 00:01:17,530
Aren't you a lousy talker?

37
00:01:18,910 --> 00:01:19,590
Alright.

38
00:01:19,610 --> 00:01:20,330
Be good.

39
00:01:21,039 --> 00:01:22,070
We made a pact, didn't we?

40
00:01:22,070 --> 00:01:23,590
As a man, I should focus on my career

41
00:01:23,590 --> 00:01:25,250
and make achievements first.

42
00:01:26,310 --> 00:01:27,150
Fine then.

43
00:01:28,710 --> 00:01:30,640
I'll take it back and eat it myself.

44
00:02:06,210 --> 00:02:07,490
Armbar!

45
00:02:09,410 --> 00:02:10,850
Sorry. I did wrong.

46
00:02:10,880 --> 00:02:12,040
Did you choke?

47
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:14,810
Do you yield?

48
00:02:14,910 --> 00:02:15,470
Yes, I do.

49
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:17,460
Stop messing around then.

50
00:02:17,470 --> 00:02:19,240
Lie beside me for a while, will you?

51
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:21,640
I've been working overtime for three days.

52
00:02:27,450 --> 00:02:28,079
Jin,

53
00:02:28,760 --> 00:02:30,250
you smell so good.

54
00:02:31,850 --> 00:02:32,690
You bet I do.

55
00:02:33,110 --> 00:02:35,040
Your girlfriend has to smell good.

56
00:02:47,290 --> 00:02:50,360
I finally have a home of my own.

57
00:04:17,490 --> 00:04:23,190
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

58
00:04:23,550 --> 00:04:26,090
[Episode 21]

59
00:04:27,270 --> 00:04:28,070
I'm back!

60
00:04:34,510 --> 00:04:35,870
What were you talking about?

61
00:04:35,870 --> 00:04:36,680
Well...

62
00:04:36,960 --> 00:04:37,960
Just her husband.

63
00:04:40,040 --> 00:04:40,970
What's with him?

64
00:04:41,740 --> 00:04:42,370
Nothing.

65
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:43,830
He's not available for dinner

66
00:04:43,830 --> 00:04:44,760
with us tonight.

67
00:04:45,420 --> 00:04:46,030
It's okay.

68
00:04:46,050 --> 00:04:47,510
I'll go to dinner with you.

69
00:04:48,170 --> 00:04:49,500
O-Oh, forget it.

70
00:04:49,870 --> 00:04:51,040
Our head just said

71
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:52,290
you wouldn't be free either.

72
00:04:52,290 --> 00:04:52,930
He asked us

73
00:04:52,960 --> 00:04:54,159
to set out right away.

74
00:04:54,900 --> 00:04:56,230
You're leaving so soon?

75
00:04:57,510 --> 00:04:59,640
Zhou Jin, meet me out here for a second.

76
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:10,100
I need to talk to you

77
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:12,080
about a very serious matter.

78
00:05:12,510 --> 00:05:13,360
Jiang Cheng

79
00:05:13,950 --> 00:05:15,040
proposed

80
00:05:15,790 --> 00:05:17,960
to have you as his liaison officer.

81
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:20,360
I need to ask

82
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:24,190
for your opinion on this.

83
00:05:26,070 --> 00:05:27,330
Don't force yourself.

84
00:05:27,400 --> 00:05:28,860
If you don't consent to it,

85
00:05:28,950 --> 00:05:29,880
I'll tell him no.

86
00:05:40,310 --> 00:05:41,640
I'm not forcing myself.

87
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:44,290
I'll take the job and do it well.

88
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,360
What are these?

89
00:06:17,070 --> 00:06:18,190
Some daily necessities

90
00:06:18,190 --> 00:06:19,720
I ordered for you on the way.

91
00:06:19,920 --> 00:06:20,810
If you need anything else,

92
00:06:20,810 --> 00:06:21,760
just let me know.

93
00:06:28,920 --> 00:06:30,270
I feel like it has been a lifetime

94
00:06:30,270 --> 00:06:31,470
since I was last here.

95
00:06:40,230 --> 00:06:40,960
The rent

96
00:06:41,350 --> 00:06:43,210
is paid up till the end of the year.

97
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:45,159
Just live here without worries.

98
00:07:23,430 --> 00:07:24,600
I am finally home.

99
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:52,520
There are daily necessities in these bags,

100
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:55,040
including toothbrushes, tissues,

101
00:07:55,270 --> 00:07:56,240
and some food.

102
00:07:56,950 --> 00:07:57,610
And this...

103
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:59,720
What food did you buy me?

104
00:08:00,070 --> 00:08:02,330
Any buns with preserved mustard greens?

105
00:08:03,410 --> 00:08:05,120
Let me put these away for you.

106
00:08:37,650 --> 00:08:39,039
You didn't use to be like this.

107
00:08:39,039 --> 00:08:40,610
Since when did you become so particular

108
00:08:40,610 --> 00:08:42,140
about where everything...

109
00:09:22,790 --> 00:09:23,790
Do you need a hand?

110
00:09:29,180 --> 00:09:30,110
Dinner is ready.

111
00:09:30,440 --> 00:09:31,240
Eat it then.

112
00:09:33,530 --> 00:09:34,730
Won't you eat with me?

113
00:09:36,360 --> 00:09:37,620
I'll eat at home later.

114
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:53,550
I didn't prepare much today
on such short notice.

115
00:09:53,550 --> 00:09:55,120
Whatever else you need later,

116
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:56,050
just let me know.

117
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:57,560
I'll order it for you.

118
00:10:19,550 --> 00:10:20,680
I need to go home now.

119
00:10:25,050 --> 00:10:25,650
Jin,

120
00:10:26,560 --> 00:10:28,130
I've never betrayed you.

121
00:10:29,280 --> 00:10:31,040
I haven't been with another woman
in these five years,

122
00:10:31,040 --> 00:10:32,070
not even once.

123
00:10:34,480 --> 00:10:35,440
I know...

124
00:10:35,670 --> 00:10:37,080
I know that former incident

125
00:10:37,080 --> 00:10:38,390
has left you deeply traumatized.

126
00:10:38,390 --> 00:10:39,030
But

127
00:10:39,030 --> 00:10:40,360
I didn't do anything.

128
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:42,000
I swear to God.

129
00:10:45,360 --> 00:10:46,290
That doesn't...

130
00:10:48,030 --> 00:10:48,960
matter anymore.

131
00:10:51,260 --> 00:10:53,060
Is it because of Jiang Hansheng?

132
00:10:54,670 --> 00:10:56,400
How long have you been with him?

133
00:10:56,590 --> 00:10:57,590
Do you even know him?

134
00:10:57,590 --> 00:10:59,920
What's the fun of being with a guy
like him?

135
00:11:10,370 --> 00:11:11,230
Do you like him?

136
00:11:16,150 --> 00:11:17,210
Then what about me?

137
00:11:17,670 --> 00:11:18,800
Do you still like me?

138
00:11:20,870 --> 00:11:22,630
Don't do this, Jiang Cheng.

139
00:11:22,630 --> 00:11:23,750
Tell me the truth!

140
00:11:43,650 --> 00:11:44,410
Why?

141
00:11:50,110 --> 00:11:50,660
I...

142
00:11:55,190 --> 00:11:56,470
can't persuade myself

143
00:11:59,400 --> 00:12:00,670
to like you again.

144
00:12:00,700 --> 00:12:01,580
But you can!

145
00:12:01,960 --> 00:12:03,150
As long as you want to,

146
00:12:03,150 --> 00:12:04,840
we can go back to how things were!

147
00:12:04,840 --> 00:12:05,960
We can make that happen!

148
00:12:05,960 --> 00:12:07,030
There is no "us" anymore,

149
00:12:07,030 --> 00:12:07,910
Jiang Cheng.

150
00:12:09,510 --> 00:12:10,750
We're over.

151
00:12:14,600 --> 00:12:16,330
There's no way of turning back.

152
00:12:17,870 --> 00:12:18,750
I know

153
00:12:19,670 --> 00:12:21,470
everything you did was for me.

154
00:12:23,460 --> 00:12:25,120
If there's anything you need,

155
00:12:26,190 --> 00:12:27,500
I'll always help.

156
00:12:42,020 --> 00:12:43,680
Do you think I went undercover

157
00:12:44,510 --> 00:12:46,510
just to make you feel guilty about me

158
00:12:47,510 --> 00:12:48,840
so you would compensate

159
00:12:49,080 --> 00:12:49,630
me?

160
00:12:52,960 --> 00:12:53,510
Jin,

161
00:12:55,550 --> 00:12:56,810
I hope you can be happy.

162
00:12:59,910 --> 00:13:00,550
I hope...

163
00:13:01,610 --> 00:13:03,560
you can care for me like you used to.

164
00:13:08,870 --> 00:13:10,150
I'm sorry.

165
00:13:12,790 --> 00:13:14,390
I-I'm really sorry.

166
00:13:20,790 --> 00:13:22,190
So all there is left to say

167
00:13:25,030 --> 00:13:26,790
between us is "sorry" now,

168
00:13:27,630 --> 00:13:28,440
right?

169
00:13:46,100 --> 00:13:47,690
This is my fault.

170
00:13:49,390 --> 00:13:50,790
I did terribly wrong.

171
00:13:52,510 --> 00:13:54,060
My acting was so good...

172
00:13:56,530 --> 00:13:58,980
that you thought I had really dumped you.

173
00:14:02,510 --> 00:14:04,990
It was I who pushed you away.

174
00:14:06,480 --> 00:14:08,340
It was not like that, Jiang Cheng.

175
00:14:09,250 --> 00:14:11,250
You did nothing wrong, Jiang Cheng.

176
00:14:12,680 --> 00:14:14,140
None of this is your fault.

177
00:14:16,510 --> 00:14:17,270
I mean it.

178
00:14:17,750 --> 00:14:19,480
The problem doesn't lie in you,

179
00:14:20,720 --> 00:14:22,030
but in me.

180
00:14:24,790 --> 00:14:25,320
It was...

181
00:14:28,440 --> 00:14:30,000
I who wronged you.

182
00:14:31,320 --> 00:14:32,270
I swear

183
00:14:32,740 --> 00:14:34,220
I'll do whatever I can

184
00:14:34,250 --> 00:14:35,430
to help you get reinstated.

185
00:14:35,430 --> 00:14:36,100
Okay?

186
00:14:36,790 --> 00:14:38,440
It was I who let you down.

187
00:14:39,880 --> 00:14:41,760
I'll do everything you ask me to,

188
00:14:42,950 --> 00:14:43,640
alright?

189
00:14:53,930 --> 00:14:54,930
Jiang Cheng...

190
00:15:08,440 --> 00:15:09,810
Sending a man home this late...

191
00:15:09,810 --> 00:15:10,360
Have you never

192
00:15:10,360 --> 00:15:12,090
thought what he might do to you?

193
00:15:12,360 --> 00:15:13,490
Don't do this again.

194
00:16:25,440 --> 00:16:26,270
Sorry,

195
00:16:26,390 --> 00:16:29,390
the number you dialed
cannot be reached at the moment.

196
00:16:32,750 --> 00:16:33,930
[Zhou Jin]

197
00:16:41,740 --> 00:16:42,500
Jin.

198
00:16:42,590 --> 00:16:43,080
Dad,

199
00:16:44,070 --> 00:16:45,070
where are you?

200
00:16:45,100 --> 00:16:47,030
I'm coming to pick up Hansheng now.

201
00:16:47,200 --> 00:16:47,960
Where are we?

202
00:16:48,250 --> 00:16:49,770
I'm home with Fang.

203
00:16:50,750 --> 00:16:52,080
Hansheng isn't with us.

204
00:16:52,280 --> 00:16:54,010
He said you would be busy today.

205
00:16:56,030 --> 00:16:56,840
Oh, I see.

206
00:16:57,920 --> 00:16:59,100
I was indeed a bit busy today,

207
00:16:59,100 --> 00:17:01,490
occupied by something.
But now the work's all done.

208
00:17:01,490 --> 00:17:03,020
So I want to come pick him up.

209
00:17:03,380 --> 00:17:04,619
Being busy is a good thing

210
00:17:04,619 --> 00:17:05,619
for young people.

211
00:17:06,390 --> 00:17:08,349
Well, I'll head home then.

212
00:17:08,369 --> 00:17:11,000
I'll come visit you and Auntie Fang
some other day.

213
00:17:11,000 --> 00:17:12,000
Okay.

214
00:17:12,160 --> 00:17:13,270
Come over anytime

215
00:17:13,270 --> 00:17:14,400
when you are free.

216
00:17:16,160 --> 00:17:17,220
I'm hanging up now.

217
00:17:17,240 --> 00:17:17,680
Okay.

218
00:17:17,960 --> 00:17:18,550
Bye.

219
00:19:04,320 --> 00:19:05,950
Qi, my dear Qi,

220
00:19:07,160 --> 00:19:08,160
I was wondering

221
00:19:08,160 --> 00:19:09,820
why you had to stay in Haizhou.

222
00:19:10,560 --> 00:19:12,760
It turns out you meant to get even for me.

223
00:19:14,960 --> 00:19:15,530
Love you.

224
00:19:43,880 --> 00:19:44,610
Hansheng...

225
00:19:48,030 --> 00:19:48,880
Hansheng...

226
00:19:50,640 --> 00:19:51,370
Hansheng...

227
00:19:55,490 --> 00:19:56,950
Professor Jiang is on the way here.

228
00:19:56,950 --> 00:19:58,010
He'll arrive soon.

229
00:20:00,480 --> 00:20:01,070
Dan.

230
00:20:01,600 --> 00:20:02,400
How are you?

231
00:20:06,880 --> 00:20:07,550
I'm fine.

232
00:20:10,460 --> 00:20:11,920
Consider yourself lucky.

233
00:20:12,050 --> 00:20:13,890
Good thing you reacted fast
and were driving fast.

234
00:20:13,890 --> 00:20:15,660
That truck only hit the rear of your car,

235
00:20:15,660 --> 00:20:16,790
so you weren't hurt.

236
00:20:19,920 --> 00:20:20,510
Hello.

237
00:20:20,680 --> 00:20:22,400
Where is Zhou Jin? She's in Bed 11.

238
00:20:22,400 --> 00:20:23,350
The second room in there.

239
00:20:23,350 --> 00:20:23,880
Thanks.

240
00:20:25,350 --> 00:20:26,880
Are you Zhou Jin's husband?

241
00:20:27,110 --> 00:20:27,870
Yes, I am.

242
00:20:28,790 --> 00:20:30,440
Here's a package for you.

243
00:20:32,870 --> 00:20:33,790
Who sent it?

244
00:20:34,070 --> 00:20:35,130
Some delivery guy.

245
00:20:48,650 --> 00:20:50,500
[Professor Jiang, let's play the game
another way]

246
00:20:50,500 --> 00:20:52,360
[I'll hurt whoever you try to protect.
Is it fun?]

247
00:21:11,790 --> 00:21:13,750
Where can I watch
the surveillance footage?

248
00:21:13,750 --> 00:21:15,880
I'm really fine. Don't worry about me.

249
00:21:15,890 --> 00:21:17,020
I'm perfectly well.

250
00:21:22,590 --> 00:21:23,550
I can get off work now,

251
00:21:23,550 --> 00:21:25,010
as he's here to replace me.

252
00:21:25,440 --> 00:21:26,870
Your husband's waiting downstairs, right?

253
00:21:26,870 --> 00:21:27,830
Yes, exactly.

254
00:21:28,550 --> 00:21:29,280
Don't worry.

255
00:21:29,440 --> 00:21:31,170
The doctor said she's all fine.

256
00:21:31,680 --> 00:21:32,540
I'll take off then.

257
00:21:32,540 --> 00:21:34,020
Hansheng, walk Dan out.

258
00:21:34,320 --> 00:21:35,880
No need. I'm good on my own.

259
00:21:38,600 --> 00:21:40,130
Sorry for the trouble, Dan.

260
00:21:57,230 --> 00:21:58,400
Why just stand there?

261
00:21:58,400 --> 00:21:59,030
Come here.

262
00:22:10,870 --> 00:22:11,750
Does it hurt?

263
00:22:13,680 --> 00:22:14,400
Yes.

264
00:22:15,440 --> 00:22:16,640
It hurts a lot.

265
00:22:17,210 --> 00:22:18,610
My shoulders are aching,

266
00:22:18,770 --> 00:22:20,370
and my head is buzzing.

267
00:22:21,090 --> 00:22:22,350
Where else is hurting?

268
00:22:23,480 --> 00:22:25,010
Every other part of my body.

269
00:22:25,680 --> 00:22:27,590
I feel like I can't move at all.

270
00:22:33,240 --> 00:22:34,030
Don't just stand there.

271
00:22:34,030 --> 00:22:34,720
Take a seat.

272
00:22:45,920 --> 00:22:46,720
What is it

273
00:22:47,070 --> 00:22:47,960
with you?

274
00:22:49,310 --> 00:22:50,640
You're acting strange.

275
00:22:57,490 --> 00:22:59,140
Did my master run his mouth

276
00:22:59,480 --> 00:23:00,810
and tell you something?

277
00:23:04,160 --> 00:23:04,880
Hansheng,

278
00:23:05,510 --> 00:23:07,310
I must confess something to you.

279
00:23:08,640 --> 00:23:09,310
Today,

280
00:23:11,590 --> 00:23:13,310
I dropped by my old apartment

281
00:23:14,350 --> 00:23:15,350
with Jiang Cheng.

282
00:23:16,350 --> 00:23:17,110
I brought him there

283
00:23:17,110 --> 00:23:19,050
only because he has nowhere to live now.

284
00:23:19,050 --> 00:23:20,400
The team approved of him

285
00:23:20,430 --> 00:23:21,950
staying there for a while.

286
00:23:22,400 --> 00:23:23,590
So I went there with him

287
00:23:23,590 --> 00:23:25,050
and tidied things up a bit.

288
00:23:27,400 --> 00:23:28,240
It was just one hour.

289
00:23:28,240 --> 00:23:29,550
I only spent one hour with him.

290
00:23:29,550 --> 00:23:30,110
Really.

291
00:23:30,200 --> 00:23:31,160
I left right after.

292
00:23:31,160 --> 00:23:32,220
Nothing happened.

293
00:23:32,400 --> 00:23:33,200
Rest assured.

294
00:23:41,960 --> 00:23:42,690
That's nice.

295
00:23:46,920 --> 00:23:49,380
Jiang Cheng is truly able
to take care of you.

296
00:23:50,820 --> 00:23:51,750
Jiang Hansheng,

297
00:23:53,750 --> 00:23:55,430
do you even hear yourself?

298
00:24:06,960 --> 00:24:07,720
Zhou Jin,

299
00:24:10,720 --> 00:24:11,480
I love you.

300
00:24:17,340 --> 00:24:17,970
Hansheng,

301
00:24:19,910 --> 00:24:21,710
I know I've been behaving poorly

302
00:24:22,610 --> 00:24:23,780
these days.

303
00:24:23,810 --> 00:24:24,870
We should split up.

304
00:24:28,880 --> 00:24:29,680
What?

305
00:24:34,790 --> 00:24:35,920
Let's get a divorce.

306
00:24:37,310 --> 00:24:38,510
I'm serious about it.

307
00:24:51,540 --> 00:24:52,170
Hansheng,

308
00:24:52,510 --> 00:24:53,030
I...

309
00:24:53,030 --> 00:24:54,160
I know I haven't played the part

310
00:24:54,160 --> 00:24:55,560
of a good wife these days.

311
00:24:55,750 --> 00:24:57,550
I've neglected your feelings.

312
00:24:57,550 --> 00:24:57,960
But...

313
00:24:57,960 --> 00:24:59,820
You're not in the wrong, Zhou Jin.

314
00:25:01,480 --> 00:25:02,740
This isn't your fault.

315
00:25:04,160 --> 00:25:05,420
The problem is with me.

316
00:25:06,720 --> 00:25:08,000
We're not right for each other.

317
00:25:08,000 --> 00:25:09,600
What's the problem with you?

318
00:25:10,030 --> 00:25:11,030
How are we not right for each other?

319
00:25:11,030 --> 00:25:12,960
Have you ever asked for my opinion?

320
00:25:13,500 --> 00:25:15,630
Everything's perfectly fine with us.

321
00:25:16,330 --> 00:25:17,260
What is going on?

322
00:25:21,510 --> 00:25:22,160
Zhou Jin.

323
00:25:24,900 --> 00:25:27,230
You've only grown used
to me being around.

324
00:25:27,850 --> 00:25:29,400
But habits can be broken easily.

325
00:25:29,400 --> 00:25:31,480
Jiang Hansheng, what's wrong with you?

326
00:25:31,480 --> 00:25:33,140
Why are you spewing nonsense?

327
00:25:44,270 --> 00:25:46,200
Zhou Jin, let me ask you a question.

328
00:25:47,680 --> 00:25:49,920
No need to take my feelings
into consideration.

329
00:25:49,920 --> 00:25:51,520
Just give me a candid answer.

330
00:25:55,350 --> 00:25:56,030
Ask away.

331
00:26:01,640 --> 00:26:02,480
If you had known

332
00:26:02,480 --> 00:26:04,680
Jiang Cheng's identity from the start,

333
00:26:05,720 --> 00:26:08,180
would I have stood any chance
with you at all?

334
00:26:19,570 --> 00:26:20,500
There are no ifs.

335
00:26:20,840 --> 00:26:21,470
Answer me.

336
00:26:21,710 --> 00:26:22,570
I don't want to.

337
00:26:37,640 --> 00:26:38,970
We both know the answer.

338
00:26:41,270 --> 00:26:42,200
Jiang Hansheng,

339
00:26:43,030 --> 00:26:43,640
you are

340
00:26:44,510 --> 00:26:46,240
being jealous in the wrong way.

341
00:26:49,790 --> 00:26:51,440
We are already married.

342
00:26:51,550 --> 00:26:53,680
It's good that Jiang Cheng is back now.

343
00:26:54,200 --> 00:26:54,880
This way,

344
00:26:55,720 --> 00:26:57,320
things will be easier for us.

345
00:26:59,160 --> 00:27:01,820
You won't be shackled
by this marriage anymore.

346
00:27:03,240 --> 00:27:04,770
Are you deciding for me now?

347
00:27:07,350 --> 00:27:08,680
I will pack up your stuff

348
00:27:09,350 --> 00:27:10,950
and put it in the police dorm.

349
00:27:11,350 --> 00:27:12,810
Before the case is solved,

350
00:27:13,070 --> 00:27:14,330
you should stay there.

351
00:27:15,030 --> 00:27:16,490
Let's be apart for a while.

352
00:27:17,550 --> 00:27:19,070
We're getting a divorce anyway.

353
00:27:19,070 --> 00:27:20,870
Why even bother where I'll stay?

354
00:27:24,400 --> 00:27:25,030
Whatever.

355
00:27:26,630 --> 00:27:28,560
Jiang Hansheng, stop right there!

356
00:27:31,400 --> 00:27:33,460
You're a real character, aren't you?

357
00:27:34,640 --> 00:27:35,290
Back then,

358
00:27:35,960 --> 00:27:38,690
I proposed marriage to you
in this very hospital.

359
00:27:38,720 --> 00:27:39,480
And now,

360
00:27:39,750 --> 00:27:42,250
you're asking for a divorce
in the same place, huh?

361
00:27:42,250 --> 00:27:43,360
Do you remember

362
00:27:43,860 --> 00:27:45,090
what you promised me?

363
00:27:47,250 --> 00:27:47,970
You said

364
00:27:49,270 --> 00:27:50,530
you would never hurt me

365
00:27:51,070 --> 00:27:52,440
or betray me.

366
00:27:54,480 --> 00:27:55,610
Have you forgotten?

367
00:27:58,550 --> 00:27:59,110
Zhou Jin,

368
00:28:00,640 --> 00:28:01,440
I promise you.

369
00:28:02,510 --> 00:28:03,510
I won't hurt you

370
00:28:04,400 --> 00:28:05,480
or betray you.

371
00:28:15,880 --> 00:28:16,590
Sorry.

372
00:28:17,880 --> 00:28:18,940
I broke my promise.

373
00:28:20,480 --> 00:28:21,240
Jiang Hansheng!

374
00:28:21,240 --> 00:28:25,080
♪ I never want you to bear the pain ♪

375
00:28:22,880 --> 00:28:24,000
Jiang Hansheng, don't you dare go!

376
00:28:24,000 --> 00:28:24,790
What happened?

377
00:28:24,790 --> 00:28:26,400
You can't leave the ward yet.

378
00:28:28,490 --> 00:28:33,090
♪ I'm about to exhaust all I have ♪

379
00:28:35,840 --> 00:28:39,590
♪ Trading time with touching moments ♪

380
00:28:40,350 --> 00:28:43,430
♪ Look at the fish
swimming in the ocean depths ♪

381
00:28:45,350 --> 00:28:47,580
♪ They're so free ♪

382
00:28:49,820 --> 00:28:52,900
♪ How can I tell you ♪

383
00:28:52,920 --> 00:28:56,550
♪ How much I love you with a smile ♪

384
00:28:57,220 --> 00:29:00,040
♪ I am sure to ♪

385
00:29:00,080 --> 00:29:03,620
♪ Walk with you ♪

386
00:29:02,160 --> 00:29:03,270
My phone...

387
00:29:04,650 --> 00:29:08,120
♪ I look at you day and night ♪

388
00:29:08,000 --> 00:29:08,960
Where's my phone?

389
00:29:08,150 --> 00:29:12,270
♪ One more glance is not enough ♪

390
00:29:12,290 --> 00:29:14,510
♪ At the crossroad ♪

391
00:29:13,720 --> 00:29:16,270
Where is my phone?

392
00:29:14,540 --> 00:29:17,910
♪ To the left or right ♪

393
00:29:18,910 --> 00:29:22,830
♪ I want to hold your hand ♪

394
00:29:43,350 --> 00:29:44,550
Why did you come here?

395
00:29:46,240 --> 00:29:47,900
Do you not like living with me?

396
00:29:48,220 --> 00:29:51,300
♪ How can I tell you ♪

397
00:29:49,880 --> 00:29:51,320
Do you still have feelings for him?

398
00:29:51,320 --> 00:29:54,950
♪ How much I love you with a smile ♪

399
00:29:53,160 --> 00:29:54,220
How is Jiang Cheng?

400
00:29:55,110 --> 00:29:56,510
I know you've been worried about him.

401
00:29:55,620 --> 00:29:58,440
♪ I am sure to ♪

402
00:29:57,920 --> 00:29:58,720
Don't worry.

403
00:29:58,480 --> 00:30:02,020
♪ Walk with you ♪

404
00:29:59,960 --> 00:30:00,890
I'll be with you.

405
00:30:01,880 --> 00:30:02,880
Over these years,

406
00:30:03,050 --> 00:30:06,520
♪ I look at you day and night ♪

407
00:30:04,160 --> 00:30:05,760
you've really changed a lot.

408
00:30:06,550 --> 00:30:10,110
♪ Every minute and second with you
is not a luxury ♪

409
00:30:10,480 --> 00:30:11,400
Please sit down.

410
00:30:10,610 --> 00:30:12,200
♪ At the crossroad ♪

411
00:30:12,230 --> 00:30:15,930
♪ To the left or right ♪

412
00:30:13,640 --> 00:30:14,480
If you had known

413
00:30:14,480 --> 00:30:16,680
Jiang Cheng's identity from the start,

414
00:30:17,500 --> 00:30:20,640
♪ We'll eventually hold hands ♪

415
00:30:17,640 --> 00:30:20,100
would I have stood any chance
with you at all?

416
00:30:51,550 --> 00:30:52,640
Grandpa,

417
00:30:52,640 --> 00:30:54,480
why haven't you come see me?

418
00:30:54,480 --> 00:30:57,400
When will you finish catching bad guys?

419
00:30:58,590 --> 00:30:59,680
Sweetheart,

420
00:30:59,920 --> 00:31:01,440
when I'm done catching bad guys,

421
00:31:01,440 --> 00:31:02,510
I'll go be with you.

422
00:31:04,310 --> 00:31:06,510
Okay, Grandpa. Go to bed early.

423
00:31:07,880 --> 00:31:08,680
I'll obey.

424
00:31:08,700 --> 00:31:09,780
I will.

425
00:31:13,240 --> 00:31:13,750
Dad,

426
00:31:14,030 --> 00:31:15,350
it's me, Li.

427
00:31:16,550 --> 00:31:18,110
I need to tell you something.

428
00:31:18,110 --> 00:31:20,130
Chief Zhan from the Information Department
just had a baby.

429
00:31:20,130 --> 00:31:20,970
He's holding

430
00:31:21,000 --> 00:31:22,830
a one-month celebration
at Longxing Hotel in a few days.

431
00:31:22,830 --> 00:31:25,030
He has always wanted to invite you to it.

432
00:31:25,400 --> 00:31:26,920
Why don't you

433
00:31:26,920 --> 00:31:28,000
take some time out for it?

434
00:31:28,000 --> 00:31:29,310
His baby is so adorable.

435
00:31:29,310 --> 00:31:29,920
Well,

436
00:31:30,510 --> 00:31:32,920
I'm not familiar with those
in the Information Department.

437
00:31:32,920 --> 00:31:34,680
I'd rather not attend the event.

438
00:31:34,680 --> 00:31:35,720
Listen, Dad.

439
00:31:36,440 --> 00:31:38,240
Chief Zhan is above me after all.

440
00:31:38,590 --> 00:31:40,720
I have a visitor now. Talk to you later.

441
00:31:41,590 --> 00:31:42,110
Come in!

442
00:31:59,400 --> 00:32:00,730
What are you doing here?

443
00:32:02,270 --> 00:32:02,830
Prof,

444
00:32:04,480 --> 00:32:06,410
I think I've messed everything up.

445
00:32:11,840 --> 00:32:14,030
Zhou Jin's car accident wasn't by chance.

446
00:32:14,030 --> 00:32:14,830
I've checked.

447
00:32:15,400 --> 00:32:17,200
The delivery guy who sent this over

448
00:32:17,200 --> 00:32:19,090
hid where cameras couldn't catch him.

449
00:32:19,090 --> 00:32:20,020
I can't find him.

450
00:32:25,000 --> 00:32:26,260
Are you divorcing Zhou

451
00:32:27,110 --> 00:32:28,640
just because of this?

452
00:32:32,160 --> 00:32:32,920
Pup,

453
00:32:32,950 --> 00:32:33,870
why stare at me?

454
00:32:34,110 --> 00:32:34,970
Say something.

455
00:32:40,030 --> 00:32:41,790
It's not safe for her to be with me.

456
00:32:41,790 --> 00:32:43,920
It's even less safe for her to be alone.

457
00:32:48,000 --> 00:32:49,060
She won't be alone.

458
00:32:50,310 --> 00:32:51,160
I told her

459
00:32:51,590 --> 00:32:54,000
to stay in the police dorm
at Nancheng Branch

460
00:32:54,000 --> 00:32:55,130
and never come back.

461
00:32:59,750 --> 00:33:02,270
So you ran away from home

462
00:33:02,270 --> 00:33:04,550
and came to my place in the rain.

463
00:33:05,510 --> 00:33:06,270
Right?

464
00:33:11,110 --> 00:33:11,840
Impressive.

465
00:33:12,870 --> 00:33:14,870
You're unbelievable.

466
00:33:20,550 --> 00:33:21,110
Prof,

467
00:33:21,720 --> 00:33:22,640
hear me out.

468
00:33:23,710 --> 00:33:25,510
I want a divorce for two reasons.

469
00:33:26,160 --> 00:33:26,680
First,

470
00:33:27,660 --> 00:33:28,720
Qi Yan will only act

471
00:33:28,750 --> 00:33:30,550
crazier and crazier from now on.

472
00:33:31,210 --> 00:33:33,410
When the police destroyed
the drug factory,

473
00:33:33,410 --> 00:33:35,370
they not only rescued
Yao Weihai's undercover agent,

474
00:33:35,370 --> 00:33:36,040
but also removed

475
00:33:36,040 --> 00:33:38,370
the mole Qi Yan planted inside the police.

476
00:33:39,370 --> 00:33:40,950
One single happening of these

477
00:33:40,950 --> 00:33:42,550
was enough to infuriate him,

478
00:33:43,480 --> 00:33:44,880
let alone piling them up.

479
00:33:46,110 --> 00:33:48,510
Zhou Jin's car crash
looks like an accident

480
00:33:49,300 --> 00:33:51,300
probably just because
she reacted fast enough

481
00:33:51,300 --> 00:33:52,900
to avoid being harmed by him.

482
00:33:53,550 --> 00:33:54,510
Qi Yan once said

483
00:33:56,000 --> 00:33:57,930
he would make my life a living hell.

484
00:34:01,070 --> 00:34:03,070
I know what you're saying.

485
00:34:05,130 --> 00:34:06,590
What's the second reason?

486
00:34:13,030 --> 00:34:14,030
It's Jiang Cheng.

487
00:34:18,860 --> 00:34:20,840
He turned back to being Officer Jiang
from Cangfeng.

488
00:34:20,840 --> 00:34:23,570
People have basically recognized
his identity.

489
00:34:23,920 --> 00:34:24,920
He will often show up

490
00:34:24,920 --> 00:34:26,670
in Zhou Jin's life from now on.

491
00:34:31,280 --> 00:34:32,550
So,

492
00:34:32,550 --> 00:34:34,610
you wanted to play the noble guy, huh?

493
00:34:36,719 --> 00:34:39,250
Then you just stood up with chivalry
and said,

494
00:34:39,920 --> 00:34:40,969
"Comrade Zhou,

495
00:34:41,880 --> 00:34:42,710
off you go.

496
00:34:43,710 --> 00:34:44,800
I'm backing out."

497
00:34:50,030 --> 00:34:51,110
I won't back out.

498
00:34:51,670 --> 00:34:53,510
I will still protect her in secret

499
00:34:53,510 --> 00:34:54,480
like I used to.

500
00:34:55,840 --> 00:34:58,000
Then you should've said to her like this:

501
00:34:58,000 --> 00:34:58,800
"Zhou Jin,

502
00:35:01,030 --> 00:35:02,000
off you go.

503
00:35:03,710 --> 00:35:04,760
I'm backing out."

504
00:35:11,590 --> 00:35:13,190
Prof, stop making fun of me.

505
00:35:13,320 --> 00:35:13,840
Jiang Hansheng,

506
00:35:13,840 --> 00:35:15,480
you broke up with Zhou

507
00:35:15,480 --> 00:35:17,710
before I could attend your wedding.

508
00:35:18,230 --> 00:35:19,830
Have you thought about this?

509
00:35:19,920 --> 00:35:20,550
The situation...

510
00:35:20,550 --> 00:35:23,760
Everything is different now from before.

511
00:35:25,440 --> 00:35:26,890
You heartlessly

512
00:35:27,590 --> 00:35:29,030
abandoned and deserted Zhou

513
00:35:29,030 --> 00:35:30,320
just like that.

514
00:35:31,110 --> 00:35:33,110
And you think you were being

515
00:35:33,800 --> 00:35:34,840
nice to her, huh?

516
00:35:40,920 --> 00:35:43,050
I only meant to free her from shackles.

517
00:35:48,340 --> 00:35:49,260
Hansheng,

518
00:35:50,450 --> 00:35:52,450
if you really divorce Zhou,

519
00:35:54,110 --> 00:35:55,550
will you stop loving her?

520
00:35:57,110 --> 00:35:59,990
Qi Yan is a sociopath.

521
00:36:01,070 --> 00:36:02,360
Do you think he cares

522
00:36:02,360 --> 00:36:04,020
if the two of you are divorced?

523
00:36:05,220 --> 00:36:06,220
Besides,

524
00:36:07,630 --> 00:36:10,290
do you wish to let Jiang Cheng
have what he wants,

525
00:36:11,000 --> 00:36:13,400
or are you actually
afraid of losing to him?

526
00:36:19,230 --> 00:36:21,830
Your care for someone may cloud
your judgment.

527
00:37:09,030 --> 00:37:09,760
You're back.

528
00:37:12,990 --> 00:37:13,860
What happened?

529
00:37:17,420 --> 00:37:19,080
I got in a fight with Hansheng.

530
00:37:19,100 --> 00:37:20,560
You got in a fight with him?

531
00:37:20,970 --> 00:37:22,370
The National Little Rose

532
00:37:22,410 --> 00:37:23,410
is quite prickly.

533
00:37:24,080 --> 00:37:25,190
He is, indeed.

534
00:37:25,670 --> 00:37:27,470
He packed my luggage quite well.

535
00:37:34,160 --> 00:37:35,620
The two of you got in a fight

536
00:37:35,890 --> 00:37:37,620
because of Jiang Cheng, right?

537
00:37:37,770 --> 00:37:38,540
I don't know.

538
00:37:39,850 --> 00:37:40,700
At first,

539
00:37:41,310 --> 00:37:43,370
I thought the reason was Jiang Cheng.

540
00:37:44,290 --> 00:37:45,510
I explained and apologized

541
00:37:45,510 --> 00:37:46,380
to Hansheng.

542
00:37:47,800 --> 00:37:48,570
Later on...

543
00:37:49,620 --> 00:37:51,220
I don't know what led to this.

544
00:37:51,730 --> 00:37:53,550
Actually, I completely understand you.

545
00:37:53,550 --> 00:37:55,330
People only have limited energy.

546
00:37:55,330 --> 00:37:57,310
You've been fully occupied by work lately

547
00:37:57,310 --> 00:37:58,680
and thus neglected Professor Jiang.

548
00:37:58,680 --> 00:38:00,020
Speaking from my own experience,

549
00:38:00,020 --> 00:38:01,590
I think he is probably asking

550
00:38:01,590 --> 00:38:02,590
for attention

551
00:38:02,960 --> 00:38:04,220
by triggering a fight.

552
00:38:04,330 --> 00:38:05,980
I thought the same.

553
00:38:06,310 --> 00:38:07,880
So told him he was being jealous

554
00:38:07,880 --> 00:38:09,400
in the wrong way.

555
00:38:09,580 --> 00:38:11,180
He and I are already married,

556
00:38:11,620 --> 00:38:13,220
but he still wants a divorce.

557
00:38:13,280 --> 00:38:14,090
Divorce?

558
00:38:15,420 --> 00:38:16,690
Impossible.

559
00:38:16,720 --> 00:38:18,250
He must be making nonsense.

560
00:38:18,910 --> 00:38:19,790
I know him well.

561
00:38:20,970 --> 00:38:22,230
He is serious about it.

562
00:38:22,710 --> 00:38:24,310
He truly wants to divorce me.

563
00:38:27,330 --> 00:38:28,160
In fact,

564
00:38:28,770 --> 00:38:30,720
as police officers,
especially female ones,

565
00:38:30,720 --> 00:38:32,070
it's really hard to strike

566
00:38:32,070 --> 00:38:34,000
a balance between family and work.

567
00:38:34,190 --> 00:38:35,520
I've been through this.

568
00:38:35,870 --> 00:38:36,910
My husband and I

569
00:38:37,170 --> 00:38:38,300
went to college together.

570
00:38:38,300 --> 00:38:39,830
We were chummy all the time.

571
00:38:39,850 --> 00:38:42,110
We didn't argue even after having a baby.

572
00:38:42,330 --> 00:38:42,940
However,

573
00:38:44,550 --> 00:38:45,410
a few years ago,

574
00:38:45,610 --> 00:38:47,180
because of my work,

575
00:38:47,960 --> 00:38:49,290
we nearly got a divorce.

576
00:38:50,370 --> 00:38:52,370
Coincidentally, during that time,

577
00:38:53,030 --> 00:38:54,490
what cases was I handling?

578
00:38:55,900 --> 00:38:56,830
Rape and murder.

579
00:38:57,190 --> 00:38:59,320
Cheating husbands killed their wives.

580
00:38:59,320 --> 00:39:02,250
As a result,
I found all males physically repulsive.

581
00:39:02,780 --> 00:39:04,720
When I was home,
everything my husband did annoyed me.

582
00:39:04,720 --> 00:39:07,180
He looked like a huge scumbag to
me in any way.

583
00:39:08,810 --> 00:39:10,010
Hilarious, isn't it?

584
00:39:12,690 --> 00:39:14,810
This actually reflects a problem.

585
00:39:15,240 --> 00:39:15,760
That is,

586
00:39:16,360 --> 00:39:19,710
bringing home negative emotions from work

587
00:39:19,860 --> 00:39:21,320
is an utterly awful thing.

588
00:39:22,750 --> 00:39:24,610
In retrospect, my husband told me

589
00:39:24,760 --> 00:39:27,280
that I was harsh on him about everything,

590
00:39:27,300 --> 00:39:28,900
and that I had a short temper.

591
00:39:29,750 --> 00:39:30,520
You see,

592
00:39:30,780 --> 00:39:32,240
between husband and wife,

593
00:39:32,280 --> 00:39:33,890
once there is a rift,

594
00:39:33,920 --> 00:39:36,180
they would even argue over trivialities

595
00:39:36,350 --> 00:39:38,440
and refuse to give in to each other.

596
00:39:38,980 --> 00:39:40,790
In the end, we got tired of arguing.

597
00:39:40,790 --> 00:39:41,920
I thought to myself,

598
00:39:41,940 --> 00:39:42,740
"Why the fuss?

599
00:39:42,810 --> 00:39:43,980
Maybe a divorce is needed,

600
00:39:43,980 --> 00:39:46,980
since we're torturing each other
by being together."

601
00:39:48,240 --> 00:39:49,970
But then you two made up, right?

602
00:39:50,320 --> 00:39:51,480
Of course we did.

603
00:39:51,570 --> 00:39:53,980
I couldn't have easily let him go,

604
00:39:54,010 --> 00:39:54,850
right?

605
00:39:55,240 --> 00:39:57,240
Do you know how we patched things up?

606
00:39:58,440 --> 00:39:59,190
One day,

607
00:39:59,810 --> 00:40:00,940
he got drunk

608
00:40:00,960 --> 00:40:02,160
and came to my office.

609
00:40:02,230 --> 00:40:03,960
That eight-foot-tall guy

610
00:40:04,290 --> 00:40:06,420
held onto my legs and cried.

611
00:40:06,450 --> 00:40:07,930
People were watching,

612
00:40:08,840 --> 00:40:09,840
yet he didn't feel embarrassed

613
00:40:09,840 --> 00:40:11,240
or fear being laughed at.

614
00:40:11,700 --> 00:40:12,700
He said to me,

615
00:40:13,900 --> 00:40:15,100
"For all these years,

616
00:40:15,330 --> 00:40:16,840
I've been supportive of your job,

617
00:40:16,840 --> 00:40:18,280
done all the housework,

618
00:40:18,460 --> 00:40:19,990
and taken care of our child.

619
00:40:20,560 --> 00:40:21,630
I'm a man, but is it wrong

620
00:40:21,630 --> 00:40:23,050
for me to ask for some love and care?

621
00:40:23,050 --> 00:40:25,200
Why do you have to divorce me?"

622
00:40:26,500 --> 00:40:27,360
At that moment,

623
00:40:28,540 --> 00:40:29,670
I suddenly realized

624
00:40:29,920 --> 00:40:30,710
that

625
00:40:32,090 --> 00:40:33,530
my behavior misled him.

626
00:40:34,750 --> 00:40:35,600
Also,

627
00:40:36,070 --> 00:40:37,280
over all those years,

628
00:40:38,120 --> 00:40:39,750
he had really suffered a lot.

629
00:40:41,920 --> 00:40:43,250
So, I decided right away

630
00:40:43,360 --> 00:40:45,280
to absolutely not divorce him.

631
00:40:50,680 --> 00:40:52,810
Dan, I understand what you're saying.

632
00:40:53,420 --> 00:40:55,220
I've done some thinking as well.

633
00:40:55,270 --> 00:40:56,730
I haven't done well enough

634
00:40:56,900 --> 00:40:58,030
as a wife these days.

635
00:40:58,800 --> 00:40:59,650
It's my fault.

636
00:41:02,420 --> 00:41:04,350
But things between me and Hansheng

637
00:41:05,710 --> 00:41:07,110
are different from those

638
00:41:07,920 --> 00:41:09,580
between you and your husband.

639
00:41:10,360 --> 00:41:11,620
We're in a somewhat...

640
00:41:12,960 --> 00:41:14,090
complex situation.

641
00:41:14,840 --> 00:41:16,360
The reason of it being complex

642
00:41:16,360 --> 00:41:17,490
lies in you, not him.

643
00:41:24,510 --> 00:41:25,960
He asked me a question,

644
00:41:26,710 --> 00:41:28,110
but I answered it poorly.

645
00:41:30,070 --> 00:41:30,960
What question?

646
00:41:31,280 --> 00:41:32,150
He asked

647
00:41:33,280 --> 00:41:34,550
how would I have chosen

648
00:41:34,710 --> 00:41:35,910
if I had known earlier

649
00:41:36,960 --> 00:41:39,160
that Jiang Cheng was an undercover cop.

650
00:41:42,000 --> 00:41:43,200
What was your answer?

651
00:41:45,760 --> 00:41:46,890
I couldn't give one.

652
00:41:48,000 --> 00:41:50,840
Neither did I have the courage
to tell him the truth.

653
00:41:50,840 --> 00:41:53,170
It definitely would've broken his heart.

654
00:41:53,960 --> 00:41:55,320
Because the truth is,

655
00:41:55,630 --> 00:41:56,710
if I had known earlier

656
00:41:56,710 --> 00:41:59,040
that Jiang Cheng was an undercover cop...

657
00:42:02,000 --> 00:42:03,930
I wouldn't have married Hansheng.

658
00:42:17,640 --> 00:42:19,000
You were both wrong.

659
00:42:19,760 --> 00:42:21,550
Professor Jiang shouldn't have asked
such a question,

660
00:42:21,550 --> 00:42:23,610
and you didn't have to answer it at all.

661
00:42:23,610 --> 00:42:25,450
Time never goes backwards.

662
00:42:25,650 --> 00:42:27,580
There aren't that many ifs in life.

663
00:42:30,440 --> 00:42:31,100
The fact...

664
00:42:32,300 --> 00:42:33,340
What is the fact?

665
00:42:34,270 --> 00:42:34,980
The fact is,

666
00:42:35,010 --> 00:42:37,390
you went through
five agonizing years alone

667
00:42:37,390 --> 00:42:39,250
until Professor Jiang showed up.

668
00:42:39,830 --> 00:42:41,160
He cherishes you.

669
00:42:41,690 --> 00:42:43,050
He gives you confidence.

670
00:42:43,050 --> 00:42:45,530
He makes you happy again.

671
00:42:48,940 --> 00:42:50,270
From your perspective,

672
00:42:50,670 --> 00:42:53,000
why did you refuse to answer his question?

673
00:42:54,180 --> 00:42:56,180
Because you care about his feelings

674
00:42:56,240 --> 00:42:57,760
and that you hate to hurt him.

675
00:42:57,760 --> 00:42:58,890
What does that mean?

676
00:43:00,490 --> 00:43:01,180
That means

677
00:43:03,570 --> 00:43:04,680
you're in love with him.
